headline: Kinder Morgan price target raised to $35 from $34 at TD Cowen
summary: TD Cowen analyst Jason Gabelman raised the firm’s price target on Kinder Morgan (KMI) to $35 from $34 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. Kinder Morgan’s Q4 EBITDA beat on natural gas, driven by strong system-wide performance, supports potential upside to FY26 guidance, especially amid cold-weather demand, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
